{
  "stem": "10162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 72.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very hard for me to pick up even one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the first few days when we went back-- these were all night shifts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to run back after 12 hours and there we were given the dinner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And with the spoon, I couldn't hold the spoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My hands were just-- I just couldn't hold it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My fingers were swollen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I complained, oh, it's so heavy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They said, you better do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because next week, you have to do 36 and the week after that, I don't know, 50 and you have to do up to, I don't know, 120 a night.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it just sounded like it's an impossibility.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned to do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I must say I did it even with ease at-- you know, I just-- it somehow-- in the first time in my life, I-- I realized that-- how, how with, with, with smarts, you can figure out how to do things.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, I flipped it this way and I flipped it that way and I just got it in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I almost liked it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just-- I felt like I was doing something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was proud of myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they picked-- at that time, they picked 1,000 young Hungarian women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we were there toward the end, was almost-- there, there were-- was no more raids even, because they were-- the American planes were constantly overhead.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes, they would come down so low that we could see the pilot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, we always had this unshakable faith that they know who we are and that we were happy when we saw the bombs falling next to us anywhere because they knew that they know who we are and they're not going to, to, to drop anything on us.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans were running right and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were just saying good, good, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so one day, they just evacuated the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started this march toward the center of Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were mostly marching in the dark at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the day time, we were in school buildings or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We also marched in day, in day time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I remember seeing so many German families on the road running in the other direction.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were just stepping on the highway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were just stepping over all kinds of possessions that people dropped or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- all the time we had no shoes while we were in this factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm glad you asked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had so-called klompen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was what the Dutch girls wear, Dutch wear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wooden-- clumps?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clogs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wooden clogs, that's what we had-- wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so it, it, it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody's toes were frozen, and it was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened was that, that we were marching already four, five days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many of us and my-- this girlfriend I had said that I don't care what they do to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm no-- won't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My feet are hurt and it's bleeding, and I cannot take another step.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm sitting down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, they would holler that whoever sits down or slows down will shoot and all these things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then suddenly, we realized that they start tearing that insignia off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once, we noticed that somebody is changing, changing into a civilian clothes, an SS woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the next thing, I hear that somebody-- there were many times-- forest that we-- were on the road side-- that somebody ran into the forest.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we said, really?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then we decided that next time we see a forest, we're running too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I wasn't the first one, maybe not even the second one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It didn't occur to me that you can do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when somebody did it-- So a few days after, we decided, next time there is a forest, we'll run in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in this forest, we were-- we ran inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But by then, we heard constantly the front behind us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard the cannons, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard the war coming right in our tracks practically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he knew those are the Americans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we ran into the forest, and we still heard these noises.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- the, the-- it was-- the day was coming to the-- to an end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were behind a-- we picked a large tree and we were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were there three or four of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And suddenly, there-- everything went quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't hear the cannons or anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were very scared the whole-- The night came, and there was no noise and nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
